BBK01.JB5003: National accounts - government consumption (price adjusted) / Seasonally and working-day adjusted / 1 / 2 / 3 /

General: 1 Source of the original data: Federal Statistical Office. - 2 Territorial definition: Germany as of 1991, prior to that western Germany. Linked over annual average of 1991 (Bundesbank calculation). - 3 Methodology: Figures are chain-linked Laspeyres indices (annual overlap). Data basis according to ESA 95.
